HEADWORD: Hoazin
<hw>Hoa"zin</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A
remarkable South American bird (<spn>Opisthocomus cristatus</spn>); the
crested touraco. By some Zoologists it is made the type of a distinct
order (<ord>Opisthocomi</ord>).</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hob</ent>⟦br⟧
